message.body: Yo, u mind if I put "visionary" on my mixtape too? Kinda like I did wit "do you"
Yo
Yeah my bad I was asleep. Gotta finish that Jawn up still . I was thinking if we made a video to have a fair theme would be cool. Dunno how is pull it off tho
Ok. Ill call u tom around 5 to discuss somw stuff
K
Copped those mics bul
Word

I'm really pissed off about this visionary track. I asked kurt to come to the studio wit me tonight to record my part m the intro to my part, n now we rnot b using the hook. So basically I just waisted my time writing wat I did..
Maybe Ur hook can work. All he wants to do is fix it up what he says is whack I told u we were gonna change it.
Wat does that have to do wit my part? N wat I put down leading into my part
Nothing . So why r u say in u wasted time. Should be able to still use it right?
How am I gonna use it if he keeps tryna get out of coming to the studio wit me?

Well I'm tryna get the studio at my house so we can all get together more easily. Its hard and frustrating to work with other ppl sometimes. I know Kurt isn't the most professional but I'm tryna do what I can to help
How come u didn't ask me to go to studio?
Because I don't need u to lead me into my part of the track. U lead kurt in n kurt leads me in
I wrote kurts part that'll lead me in
Therefore I need him there to record it
Yea but I gotta re record too. Could bang out the song all at once
Like I said, its whatever as far as I'm concerned
I told Kurt u reach in out to him and he gotta meet u halfway if we gonna make this work
Its whatever. I'm done.. whatever ya'll wana do
Well I'm still tryna get hot tracks done and make hot videos for what its worth
